-----------------

TC_Black
TC_Red
TC_Green
TC_Orange
TC_Blue
TC_Magenta
TC_Cyan
TC_White

Background colors
-----------------

TC_BlackBkg
TC_RedBkg
TC_GreenBkg
TC_OrangeBkg
TC_BlueBkg
TC_MagentaBkg
TC_CyanBkg
TC_WhiteBkg

Extras
------

TC_Default
TC_Bold
TC_Underline
TC_Blink
